{"lemma":"سَبْقَةٍ","slug":"سَبْقَةٍ","root":"س.ب.ق","root_slug":"س-ب-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ب-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18784","n18791"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18784","headword_ar":"سَبَقَهُ","root":"sbq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) but the former is of higher authority, or more usual, (O, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saboqN","text_ar":"سَبْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He preceded him; he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, got, went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came, before him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ahead of him; he outwent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outstripped, him; he had, got,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took, precedence of him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqad~amahu","text_ar":"تَقَدَّمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) in running, and in everything. (TA.) Some read, in the Kur [xxi. 27],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yasobuquwnahu biAlqawoli","text_ar":"لَا يَسْبُقُونَهُ بِالقَوْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", thus, with damm, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They say not"},{"kind":"text","text":"[anything]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without his having taught them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they say not"},{"kind":"text","text":"anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until He has said"},{"kind":"text","text":"it: originally,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yasobuiqu qawoluhumo qawolahu","text_ar":"لَا يَسْبُِقُ قَوْلُهُمْ قَوْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their saying does not precede his saying"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: this reading is from the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAbaqotuhu fasabaqotuhu","text_ar":"سَابَقْتُهُ فَسَبَقْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [expl. below,] aor. of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asobuquhu","text_ar":"اَسْبُقُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Bd.) See 3. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa Alfarasu fiY","text_ar":"سَبَقَ الفَرَسُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHalobapi","text_ar":"الحَلْبَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The horse outstripped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came in first, among those started together for a wager,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the race-ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) Hence the trad. of 'Alee,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa rasuwlu A@ll~`hi waSal~aY A^abuw bakorK waval~ava Eumaru","text_ar":"سَبَقَ رَسُولُ ا@للّٰهِ وَصَلَّى اَبُو بَكْرٍ وَثَلَّثَ عُمَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Apostle of God came in first"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the race,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and Aboo-Bekr came in next, and 'Omar came in third"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa","text_ar":"سَبَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"used in like manner with the objective complement understood means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He preceded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., as above; and hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, first, foremost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beforehand; he had,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"got, the priority,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precedence."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, one of the first"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foremost:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAbiqN","text_ar":"سَابِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabu Als~aboqi","text_ar":"قَصَبُ السَّبْقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qSb","text_ar":"قصب"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa Aln~aAsa A_ilaY AlA^amori","text_ar":"سَبَقَ النَّاسَ اـِلَى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He preceded the"},{"kind":"text","text":"other"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"people; was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, before them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had, got,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took, precedence of them; in betaking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"applying, himself to the affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) And in like manner one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu saboqN fiY","text_ar":"لَهُ سَبْقٌ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA AlA^amori","text_ar":"هٰذَا الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"To him belongs priority,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precedence, in this affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAbiqapN","text_ar":"سَابِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qudomapN","text_ar":"قُدْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.) ―         -b4-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa wahomuhu A_ilaY $aYo'K fagaliTa fiyhi","text_ar":"سَبَقَ وَهْمُهُ اـِلَى شَىْءٍ فَغَلِطَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He preconceived a thing, and therefore made a mistake,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"erred, respecting it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb, in explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duxila Ealayohi","text_ar":"دُخِلَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa *ihonuhu A_ilaY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"سَبَقَ ذِهْنُهُ اـِلَى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means in like manner (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He preconceived the thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his mind adverted hastily, before reflection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without premeditation, to the thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from what next follows.] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa A_ilayohimo","text_ar":"سَبَقَ اـِلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passed, hastily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly, to them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa A_ilayohi min~iY qawolN","text_ar":"سَبَقَ اـِلَيْهِ مِنِّى قَوْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A saying proceeded hastily, before reflection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without premeditation, to him from me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa","text_ar":"فَرَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"frT","text_ar":"فرط"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa minohu kalaAmN","text_ar":"سَبَقَ مِنْهُ كَلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speech proceeded hastily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraTa","text_ar":"فَرَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb in that art.:) [but this phrase also means, more agreeably with the primary signification of the verb, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speech proceeded previously from him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see the Kur x. 20, &c.;) and in like manner the former phrase.] See also 8. And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqahu AlqaYo'u","text_ar":"سَبَقَهُ القَىْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, all in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*rE","text_ar":"ذرع"},{"kind":"text","text":",) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqahu fiY Alxuruwji A_ilaY fiyhi","text_ar":"سَبَقَهُ فِى الخُرُوجِ اـِلَى فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The vomit came forth to his mouth before he was aware"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in that art.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa Alqalamu","text_ar":"سَبَقَ القَلَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The pen anticipated, skipping over something,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in transcribing.] ―         -b7-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqotu EalayohK","text_ar":"سَبَقْتُ عَلَيْهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I overcame him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa","text_ar":"سَبَقَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY qawomihi","text_ar":"عَلَى قَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He overcame his people in generosity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqahu fiY Alkarami","text_ar":"سَبَقَهُ فِى الكَرَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exceeded him in generosity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","Msb","K","TA","S"]},{"entry_id":"n18791","headword_ar":"سُبْقَةٌ","root":"sbq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}